  <summary>2/24/1999--Introduced.
Bleacher Safety Act of 1999 - Directs the Consumer Product Safety Commission to issue a bleacher safety standard for the production, erection, and retrofitting of bleacher and grandstand facilities to reduce the risk of children falling between guardrails and gaps in seats.</summary>
